/*+ NoMergeJoin(lt ml t) NoMergeJoin(lt ml t mc) NoMergeJoin(lt mc ml t cn) NoMergeJoin(cn lt mc ml t mk) NoMergeJoin(cn lt mc mk ml t k) NoMergeJoin(cn k lt mc mk ml t cc) NoMergeJoin(cc cn k lt mc mk ml t cct1) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cn k lt mc mk ml t cct2) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 cn k lt mc mk ml t ct) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 cn ct k lt mc mk ml t mi) */ select min(cn.name) AS producing_company,
min(lt.link) AS link_type,
min(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel
from link_type AS lt
inner join movie_link AS ml
on lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link like '%follow%'
inner join title AS t
on ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2000
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND ( cn.name like '%Film%' OR cn.name like '%Warner%')
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel'
inner join complete_cast AS cc
on t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast',
'crew')
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete'
inner join company_type AS ct
on mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
'Germany',
'Swedish',
'German');
